title: ASK ANDY:  Hustle vs. Productivity, with Andy Frisella - MFQA5
description: Which is it: Be productive, work smart, and finish your job early? Or hustle and put in the time beyond 10 to 6?  In this ASK ANDY episode of The MFCEO Project, Andy Frisella clarifies his position.
